songs.title: Ringtone
songs.lyrics: I took one of the default ringtones on the iPhone and flipped the hell out of it. One day I was downloading star wars ring times cuz i'm a huge star wars fan, and I was shuffling through and this one came up. I recorded it from my phone into Protools and that was it. This one kind of paints this "war" picture where there's a bunch of things going on but it still sort of tells a story. There's revenge. There's anxiety and anticipation, but also resolution
